refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
mixedDOMXPath::evaluate stringexpression DOMNodecontextnode
Executes the given XPath expression and returns a typed result if possible.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns a typed result if possible or a DOMNodeList 
 containing all nodes matching the given XPath expression.

  &reftitle.examples;



    Getting the count of all the english books


<?php

$doc = new DOMDocument;

$doc->load('book.xml');

$xpath = new DOMXPath($doc);

$tbody = $doc->getElementsByTagName('tbody')->item(0);

// our query is relative to the tbody node
$query = 'count(row/entry[. = "en"])';

$entries = $xpath->evaluate($query, $tbody);
echo "There are $entries english books\n";

?>


    &example.outputs;


There are 2 english books
